          <h2>Daikin Vs Mitsubishi Aer Conditionat</h2>
          
          <article id="daikin-sensira-plus-ftxf35a-rxf35a" data-review>
            <div data-review-bar>
              <h3>Daikin Sensira Plus FTXF35A/RXF35A</h3>
